ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: Specifies a code for the concept to be included or excluded.

ivardefs.name: designation_
ivardefs.desc: Additional representations for this concept when used in this value set - other languages, aliases, specialized purposes, used for particular purposes, etc.

ivardefs.name: display
ivardefs.desc: The text to display to the user for this concept in the context of this valueset. If no display is provided, then applications using the value set use the display specified for the code by the system.

properties.desc: Specifies a concept to be included or excluded.
